name: Speed Kills
description: The first picture I ever took, on May 26th 2019. This was captured using my phone because it was all I had with me at the time. I had this idea to start a cyberpunk-themed photography project and this served as my practice shot for trying to achieve a signature aesthetic. This will only be available for 1 week before the rest of the unclaimed editions are burned. By Lucius Felimus: https://www.luciusfelimus.com/
